    Description

    Illikkal Kallu is a Thalanadu located on top of the Illickal Malaa in the Kottayam district of Kerala, India.The distance from kottayam railway station to illikal kallu is 57km. Situated at around 3500 feet above sea level, Illickal Kallu is a major tourist attraction in Thalanadu. Wikipedia
    Address: Illikkal Kallu Rd, Moonnilavu, Poonjar Vadakkekara, Kerala 686586
